  - Public read for policy content
  - PDF export can be gated by authentication if required
  - CSRF protection on export actions
  - Content security policy aligned with app

- Validation:
  - Policy sections must have non-empty titles and content
  - regionNotices must have valid region codes
  - Template content must include required placeholders ({{companyName}}, {{lastUpdated}}, {{version}})

- Performance:
  - Caching policy data for a reasonable period (e.g., 60 minutes) with revalidation
  - PDF export should stream or provide a downloadable file within a few seconds for standard policy length

- Accessibility:
  - All content readable with screen readers
  - Keyboard navigable
  - ARIA labels where necessary
